a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_8419528\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_8419528\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 20, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104dtb1665702798948.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dtb1665702798948.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dtb1665702798948.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dtb1665702798948\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                                 \n DTD Wizard\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Define a new DTD in the current application model, or modify an existing DTD.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dtb1665702798948__p_d5696e1_d5697e1_d5698e1\">The DTD Wizard displays the DTD structure as a tree, with entities, fields, and nodes represented as nodes in the DTD tree.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dtb1665702798948__section_nzg_cw2_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d126586e56\">Fields</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"dtb1665702798948__ul_zzp_dw2_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dtb1665702798948__li_d2915e1_d2916e1_d2917e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xks1665702799087.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xks1665702799087.html\" title=\"This field lists the DTD items that are direct children of the tree node selected in the tree view.\">DTD Item Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dtb1665702798948__li_d2918e1_d2919e1_d2920e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uwm1665702799173.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uwm1665702799173.html\" title=\"Uniface field or entity a DTD item is mapped to. Read-only.\">Uniface Name</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dtb1665702798948__section_vlk_2w2_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d126586e83\">How to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"dtb1665702798948__ul_mzk_fw2_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dtb1665702798948__li_d2888e1_d2889e1_d2890e1\">To define or edit the elements in DTD, right-click and\n          select the desired action from the pop-up menu. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dtb1665702798948__li_d2891e1_d2892e1_d2893e1\">To generate DTD declarations from the DTD Wizard’s tree\n          structure, click <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">OK</span>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dtb1665702798948__li_d2894e1_d2895e1_d2896e1\">To discard your changes, click\n            <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Cancel</span>, and return to the Define DTD form. </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dtb1665702798948__p_d5705e1_d5706e1_d5707e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ihm1665702654967.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ihm1665702654967.html\" title=\"You can use the DTD Wizard to create DTDs based on modeled entities.\">Generating a DTD From a Modeled Entity</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dtb1665702798948__section_jxc_gw2_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d126586e117\">Pop-up Menu</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"dtb1665702798948__ul_s3f_hw2_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dtb1665702798948__li_d2897e1_d2898e1_d2899e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Insert Entity</span>—insert an entity as\n          a child of the current DTD tree node or another entity. <p class=\"p\" id=\"dtb1665702798948__p_d5711e1_d5712e1_d5713e1\">To insert entities not defined in an application model available in your Repository,\n            define the appropriate declarations in the DTD Editor.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dtb1665702798948__li_d2900e1_d2901e1_d2902e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Load Fields</span>—load the fields of an\n          entity as children of an entity node in the DTD tree. The fields must be defined for the\n          entity in the application model. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dtb1665702798948__li_d2903e1_d2904e1_d2905e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Insert Field</span>—add a field as a\n          child of an entity node. Use <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Rename Field</span> to insert fields defined\n          in your application model, or enter the name of a non-model field. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dtb1665702798948__li_d2906e1_d2907e1_d2908e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Select Attributes</span>—select\n          attributes for the current DTD tree node. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dtb1665702798948__li_d2909e1_d2910e1_d2911e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Remove</span>—remove an entity or field\n          node and all its children from the DTD tree. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dtb1665702798948__li_d2912e1_d2913e1_d2914e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Rename</span>—change the name of a\n          field, entity, or root node. Ensure that the new name is unique in the tree and that you\n          follow the naming rules specified by the XML standard. <p class=\"p\" id=\"dtb1665702798948__p_d5714e1_d5715e1_d5716e1\">When you rename a node, an entry is created in the default mapping between names of\n            elements and names of Uniface fields and entities.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nfe1665702799750.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Defining DTD Mappings</a><p>Define DTD mapping lists when you need to pass information via XML streams. You can define default mappings for modeled objects and local mappings for specific components or operations.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8419528\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8419528\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "DTD Wizard Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 DTD Wizard Define a new DTD in the current application model, or modify an existing DTD. The DTD Wizard displays the DTD structure as a tree, with entities, fields, and nodes represented as nodes in the DTD tree. Fields DTD Item Name Uniface Name How to To define or edit the elements in DTD, right-click and select the desired action from the pop-up menu. To generate DTD declarations from the DTD Wizard’s tree structure, click OK . To discard your changes, click Cancel , and return to the Define DTD form. For more information, see Generating a DTD From a Modeled Entity . Pop-up Menu Insert Entity —insert an entity as a child of the current DTD tree node or another entity. To insert entities not defined in an application model available in your Repository, define the appropriate declarations in the DTD Editor. Load Fields —load the fields of an entity as children of an entity node in the DTD tree. The fields must be defined for the entity in the application model. Insert Field —add a field as a child of an entity node. Use Rename Field to insert fields defined in your application model, or enter the name of a non-model field. Select Attributes —select attributes for the current DTD tree node. Remove —remove an entity or field node and all its children from the DTD tree. Rename —change the name of a field, entity, or root node. Ensure that the new name is unique in the tree and that you follow the naming rules specified by the XML standard. When you rename a node, an entry is created in the default mapping between names of elements and names of Uniface fields and entities. Related Links Defining DTD Mappings Define DTD mapping lists when you need to pass information via XML streams. You can define default mappings for modeled objects and local mappings for specific components or operations. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}